Number of messages where payload data was delivered to a buffer on the overflow list because there was no match on the priority list. Four counters of which 0 is the default. These messages incur higher cost because data must be copied from the overflow buffer. Compute the ratio priority/(priority + overflow) to determine the porportion of messages for which receives were posted in advance.
